NAME="capability"
SECTION="group"
SUMMARY="User's capabilities management command group"
USAGE="singularity [...] capability.<command> [...]"

print_help() {
cat<<EOF

This is a command group that supports the management of user's capabilities.

CAPABILITY GROUP COMMANDS:

    capability.list     List user's capabilities
    capability.add      Add user's capabilities
    capability.drop     Drop user's capabillities

All group commands have their own help output:

    $ singularity help capability.list
    $ singularity capability.list --help

For additional help, please visit our public documentation pages which are
found at:

    http://singularity.lbl.gov/
EOF
}
